      "letter": "a",
      "prompt": "Find the average value of the radius of the funnel.",
      "point_value": 3,
      "scoring_notes": "From scoring key: Average radius $= \\frac{1}{10}\\int_0^{10} \\frac{1}{20}(3+h^2)\\, dh = \\frac{1}{200}\\left[3h + \\frac{h^3}{3}\\right]_0^{10} = \\frac{1}{200}\\left(30 + \\frac{1000}{3}\\right) = \\frac{109}{60}$ inches.",
      "requires_drawing": false,
      "reference_image": null,
